If Heston Blumenthal is among your mom's food heroes, she's sure to be impressed that you went the extra mile and cooked some of these sophisticated dishes that require a fair bit of time, skill and effort. Lean proteins and lots of colourful fruit and veg make these dishes a winner for the mom who's on a clean-eating mission. It's the quintessential Mother's Day meal after all. These tasty dishes are the answer when you're catering for a crowd Quick, easy and requiring just a handful of ingredients, these dishes can successfully be whipped up at the last minute.